      "key": "interview_guide",
      "title": "Interview Guide",
      "description": "Interview guide for HR and Hiring Managers",
      "content": "# Interview Guide\n\n## 1. Interview Preparation\n\n- Review CV 15 minutes before\n- Prepare role-specific questions\n- Check meeting room/link\n\n## 2. Interview Structure\n\n### Phone Screen (30 minutes)\n1. Company introduction (5 min)\n2. Background questions (10 min)\n3. Motivation and expectations (10 min)\n4. Q&A (5 min)\n\n### Technical Interview (60 minutes)\n1. Technical questions (30 min)\n2. Live coding/Case study (20 min)\n3. Q&A (10 min)\n\n### Final Interview (45 minutes)\n1. Culture fit (15 min)\n2. Leadership/Teamwork (15 min)\n3. Salary negotiation (10 min)\n4. Next steps (5 min)\n\n## 3. Sample Questions\n\n### Behavioral\n- Tell me about a time when...\n- How do you handle...\n- Describe a situation where...\n\n### Technical (customize by role)\n- ...\n\n## 4. Evaluation Criteria\n\n| Criteria | Weight | Score (1-5) |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| Technical Skills | 30% | |\n| Problem Solving | 25% | |\n| Communication | 20% | |\n| Culture Fit | 15% | |\n| Leadership | 10% | |\n\n## 5. Red Flags\n\n- ‚ùå Speaking negatively about previous employers\n- ‚ùå No questions prepared\n- ‚ùå Lack of honesty\n- ‚ùå Negative attitude"
    },
